This license applies to the original build glue authored in this repository
(docker-compose.yml, .env.example, scripts, tools, tests, README.md).

This repository builds nothing from source. It pulls prebuilt images at runtime:

  - llama.cpp server (Vulkan): ghcr.io/ggml-org/llama.cpp:server-vulkan,
    upstream https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp, MIT licensed.

GGUF model weights are user-provided and mounted read-only. They are NOT part of
this repository and carry their own licenses (Gemma, Llama, Qwen, etc.). You are
responsible for complying with each model's license and acceptable-use terms.
